    {
        "id":"brightport_loudmouth",
        "message":"Hey kid, have you met my brother outside? Haha, that guy\u2019s a real Scrooge, they say we're nothing alike,  I\u2019m telling you. He\u2019s just like Mom--she\u2019d penny-pinch us for a bedtime story, and we\u2019d have to pay her with shiny stones or rainbow beetles. Hic. Speaking of bedtime stories..",
